      "text": "X: Unmei no Sentaku (Japanese: X ~運命の選択~; lit. X: Fateful Choice) is a fighting game created by Taito and Atelier Double and published by Bandai for PlayStation. Based on Madhouse's anime series X the game was released in Japan on August 22, 2002. The game features a total of ten fighters from two different groups present the X TV series who perform magic spells to take down each other.",
